data.title: Haylie’s Lunch with Nick Zano
data.meta_description: Haylie Duff was spotted out grabbing lunch at Sparkey's Restaurant in Los Angeles, California over the weekend with boyfriend Nick Zano.  The two have been apart since Haylie started filming a reality show about finding the next Elle Woods for the Broadway play.  It sure does look like they're happy to be back together!
